{"tid":2162350,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"信報大踢爆！陸軍21年1月正式攻台","createTime":"2020-08-18T05:34:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T07:53:08.000Z","uid":317202,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"d9f7c15a03ef5819e1b4d80054ba98dd3be54aa6","tid":2162350,"uid":317202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T05:34:42.000Z","msg":"【美戰機逼近東海防空識別區】<a href=\"http://bit.ly/315rRWj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F315rRWj&d=4FX4A6L%2BDQn5Srv%2BHBCkF1znTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=cfd8786e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/315rRWj</a><br />\n<br />\n解放軍在東海、台海演練之際，#美軍 一架B1B超音速戰略轟炸機周日從關島起飛，掠過台灣東北空域，逼近 #東海防空識別區，被視為針對解放軍演習的相應行動。台灣媒體認為此舉是美軍挑戰解放軍底線。<br />\n<br />\n美國海軍研究院《議事錄》期刊近日一篇評論文章預測，解放軍將於明年1月19日至21日，即美國總統交接期的3天內 #對台動武，以解決兩岸問題。文章作者是美國前參謀長聯席會議副主席、退役海軍上將溫尼菲爾德（James A. Winnefeld）和中情局前副局長莫雷爾（Michael J. Morell）。<br />\n<br />\n他們預測，大陸將在今年12月中旬起有意加劇兩岸緊張關係，隨後宣布於1月初在東海舉行大規模軍演，以掩護對台軍事調動。而解放軍長期在相關區域演習，令外界麻痹大意，同時美國大選可能對政壇產生強烈震盪，新冠肺炎疫情亦會持續影響。上述因素大為分散美國決策層注意力，最終將接受「#兩岸統一」的既定事實。<br />\n<br />\n近期台海 #擦槍走火 機率急升，《中國時報》引述台灣軍官表示，機師若未接到空軍作戰指揮部下達的命令，擅自開第一槍，自空中執勤降落後，即刻移送法辦。<br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KimNvNN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKimNvNN.png&h=4c1702f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1522b5e7c1d3edb50cd1de976950bd3f8f4eb6b0","tid":2162350,"uid":442,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T05:37:00.000Z","msg":"你地打啦。jpg"},{"pid":"1b73eab19f2a2f9c08706bf346c5a37c14cfc04d","tid":2162350,"uid":317202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T05:40:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3805fc6e7b18e426c41daaa96bd8eaef02054e4","tid":2162350,"uid":198175,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T05:41:07.000Z","msg":"如果我係台仔機師, 係台海遇到老解戰機過咗中線玩嘢, 威脅到自己或僚機安全, 我老死都打咗架支那機落嚟救自己同隊友條命先, 至多返到基地被解職處罰, 好過成為第一個被支共擊落嘅台軍機師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e54c90398598e18de00ae06cfbecfec7c9a15aa3","tid":2162350,"uid":92448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T05:44:07.000Z","msg":"即係唔打"},{"pid":"b1da571e6a9f33ca04b63ba031e4c45a9513a22e","tid":2162350,"uid":106929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T05:45:46.000Z","msg":"放風幾時打柒你<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cb3c62d4b8e3509150590a84fa6c9aacc39e2b6","tid":2162350,"uid":31215,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T05:46:49.000Z","msg":"絕密！<br />\n但連登仔都知"},{"pid":"1b8a32255e9d786f24683d07c1a490f98f9775d0","tid":2162350,"uid":317202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cb3c62d4b8e3509150590a84fa6c9aacc39e2b6","tid":2162350,"uid":31215,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T05:46:49.000Z","msg":"絕密！<br />\n但連登仔都知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T05:48:22.000Z","msg":"我呢啲足不出戶嘅廢青都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黃撚左喎"},{"pid":"7e626e58a69487506aeefe0a064f26c4d43a5a54","tid":2162350,"uid":279938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T05:48:45.000Z","msg":"佢個醬油係旺旺中國時報<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"bb4904edd7e47c7aa095d5e33257d92e49c09526","tid":2162350,"uid":107927,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T05:48:50.000Z","msg":"如果個信報記者被中共以公開軍事機密為名，用國安法拉左，我就信了"},{"pid":"e66fb97f3983d07b15de2ec8f0a42e1ca7